<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> 470015: Too many failing nozzles during WF calibration</b> </title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-B617C68B-33E8-447D-B832-572CFDE22B4F"><p class="- topic/p ">Too many nozzles failed on the mentioned printhead to be able to calculate the correct waveforms. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No actions are required unless the print quality is out of specification</b>.
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-9A8D1D75-6223-45BE-A915-08194C683433" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "> 
<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Calibration step</u> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This error is generated during the calibration step: "PrintheadWaveforms" which is part of the printhead calibration sequence.
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Patterns in calibration print</u> 
</p><table id="GUID-13E02C2D-CEC9-409B-93F0-BD0159C62DB5" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="8.19*" class="- topic/colspec "/><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">C1640/C1650
